txt.en: Ereblen can be found at Echad Uial.\n\nYou should bring the lost relics to Ereblen.
Lost relics can be found in Eithel Gwaur, the Filth-well.\n\nYou should collect lost relics.

'Many horrid things hide within the Filth-well of Eithel Gwaur, once a water-house of Gondor. Perhaps some relics of Gondor's past still rest within. If you are to venture inside, I ask of you to collect these lost relics.'
There is much for the White Company to accomplish in reclaiming Minas Ithil from the remnants of Sauron's forces.
'I see that you have success! I will ensure these relics are brought back to Minas Tirith at once. Thank you, [placeholder]. You have done Gondor a great service today.'
